reviews.text: Cosy, local restaurant offering inexpensive dishes. Table for up to 12 people but only two of them are such. Don't expect any signature dish, but meal which most of the locals would enjoy every day.

Never try their lunch & dinner before, but the breakfast is okay, they got a great variety of choice and servre until 11:30am. Regarding the cleanliness, I think it is not that bad for such a small neighbourhood restaurant. By the way, the servants here are friendly too.
Fast food, not great
small set lunch, oily steamed chicken
Breakfast here is OK, staffs are friendly, but the restaurant is dirty

reviews.text: 可提前電話訂座 要求更高質素食材 廚師功夫中上 炒粉麵能做到碟底冇油 香口
今日中午去到皇寶、伙記用水把我下半身裙衭倒到濕透、一點歉意都冇、我以後都唔會再去、希望佢哋早D結業！

吃了這間我私房菜，菜式都預訂的，亦可定人頭費用再定菜式。

最先來的豬肺湯最合我口味，值得再來。
其他的份量大，味道亦可。

適合一班好友大吃大喝。
吃唔落口，無味
食多兩個月又結業
